{"tid":1081464,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB有資源同埋有錢搞大灣區節目，有線電視主席邱達昌先生你點搞大灣區節目?","createTime":"2019-03-28T09:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T14:00:40.000Z","uid":93783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b87b90d46877ad8f0c35731f54fe9f5d5255ac83","tid":1081464,"uid":93783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:53:08.000Z","msg":"人地TVB每年製作費都1X-2X億，, 人地係有資源同埋有錢搞大灣區節目。遲D仲話可能起埋廠。<br />\n<br />\n有線電視主席邱達昌先生同鄭家純先生 你地一蚊都無出過，你點搞大灣區節目? 你邱達昌先生仲要係訪問話一定要做多啲大灣區節目！ <br />\n<br />\n你地呢兩個仆街又唔出錢，又唔注資，你地連香港市場仲未搞得掂，又唔出足花紅俾有線員工，你點搞大灣區節目?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190319/large/1552997989_1df5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190319%2Flarge%2F1552997989_1df5.jpg&h=424bf784&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c581112add7823af0e672979befab11ceda06944","tid":1081464,"uid":143380,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:15:14.000Z","msg":"樓主好撚想睇大灣區節目？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e122e943b4c9ebd99f73c60113246dd13c4c125","tid":1081464,"uid":93783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c581112add7823af0e672979befab11ceda06944","tid":1081464,"uid":143380,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:15:14.000Z","msg":"樓主好撚想睇大灣區節目？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T13:59:23.000Z","msg":"唔係 只係想講 你無錢就唔好搞大灣區節目"},{"pid":"dfeae585b56ba68a6f38e3cdc0f6b45a953de168","tid":1081464,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}